room_title: Escape room "Joker's Revenge" by Escape Room NJ in New York
room_description:
The Joker has lured you into the Funhouse with an invitation to a party, who can resist a party?! 
Some parties you would die just to get into, this one will die if you don't get out! You have 60 Minutes to figure out all of his many riddles, puzzles and mental challenges and stop the Toxic nerve agent from being released into your room and making it very hard to breathe.....
